Conclusion:
The insights derived from the customer behaviour analysis and exploratory data paint a clear picture of where business opportunities lie. By focusing on high-value customers, seasonal promotions, product-specific campaigns, and optimizing payment methods, the business can continue to thrive and scale efficiently. Actionable, targeted strategies based on this analysis will not only increase sales but also enhance customer loyalty and retention in the long term.

